downloadTitle: Microsoft Identity Manager 2016 Service Pack 1 update package
downloadDescription: Microsoft Update Package for MIM2016 SP1
detailsSection: MIM 2016 RTM Versions to update their infrastructure to the latest SP1 Build without complete uninstall. Customers already on MIM 2016 SP1 (4.4.1237) can not install this patch.
systemRequirementsSection:
MIM 2016 RTM or one of the following hotfix builds:
4.3.2064.0
4.3.2195.0
4.3.2266.0
installInstructionSection: Preform a backup of your data, and install the msp from an administrative command prompt. Visit the documentation site for more information.
